name: Unidentified Fishing Organization
description:
Catch and sell fish to upgrade your ship and keep it fueled. Don't let your fuel run out!

Created for 3 day long game jam Mini Jam 91 "UFO" with "Fish as a Mechanic"

Most Art, Font - Kenney
Backgrounds - Screaming Brain Studios
Underwater Theme - CleytonKauffman
